    "description": "本課程以銜接影視業界最新趨勢為主，期望培育具專業能力之人才。",
    "prerequisites": "需已修畢基礎影像製作及剪接學課程，方得選修本課",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "一、目前影視新潮流介紹<br>二、新的影視科技如何打破傳統敘事手法<br>三、實務範例分析<br>四、3D影像概念<br>五、VR影像概念<br>六、後製調光調色<br>七、後製特效合成<br>八、提升影片品質的技巧<br>九、輸出多元規格影像檔之流程<br>十、國際影視新潮流現況介紹<br>",
        "en": "This course is designed to provide students with the opportunity to build, acquire, and utilize an understanding of the 360-degree video production process. Students will be required to develop more sophisticated and complex productions using special computer graphics software. Advanced Video Production will give students the chance to creatively extend their basic editing skills while utilizing more advanced videography techniques through the use of multi camcorders."
    },
